# Micro Games – Project Context

## Modules

| Module | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| **micro-games-api** | `MicroGame`, `@MicroGameProperties`, `MicroGamesApi`, `MicroGamesProvider` – contract for game JARs |
| **micro-games-plugin** | Paper plugin (Core) – loads game JARs via ClassLoader |

## API Access

- **MicroGamesProvider.api** – Entry point for games and other code (McLib pattern)
- Plugin sets `MicroGamesProvider.setApi(...)` on enable, `clearApi()` on disable

## Loading

- **GameLoader** scans `plugins/MicroGames/games/` for JAR files
- Per JAR: `URLClassLoader` with parent = API classloader
- Discovery via `ServiceLoader` (`META-INF/services/net.developertobi.game.api.game.MicroGame`)
- `onLoad()` on enable, `onUnload()` on disable

## Game JAR Contract

1. Implement `MicroGame` with parameterless constructor
2. Provide `META-INF/services/net.developertobi.game.api.game.MicroGame` with fully qualified class name
